## Early game

**Kadesh** on Mars (Dark Sector Defense) is an accessible early Fieldron
Sample spot. Fieldron Sample is in Mars' region resource pool, so it drops
from the enemies you kill each round; a Resource Drop Booster and a loot frame
add to every wave, and the Dark Sector's resource-chance bonus helps too.

## Mid & late game

**Kelashin** on Neptune (Dark Sector Survival) is the wiki's recommended
endgame spot — Neptune is another Fieldron Sample planet, and its Infested
density drops the resource as enemy loot. Because it's an enemy drop, a
Resource Drop Booster, the Steel Path passive and a Nekros loot squad all
stack, so long Survival rotations with a high kill count give the best yield.

